"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/hover\">hover</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/inverted-colors\">inverted-colors</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/monochrome\">monochrome</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/orientation\">orientation</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/overflow-block\">overflow-block</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/overflow-inline\">overflow-inline</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/pointer\">pointer</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/prefers-color-scheme\">prefers-color-scheme</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/prefers-contrast\">prefers-contrast</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/prefers-reduced-data\">prefers-reduced-data</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/prefers-reduced-motion\">prefers-reduced-motion</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/resolution\">resolution</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/scripting\">scripting</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/shape\">shape</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/update-frequency\">update</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/video-dynamic-range\">video-dynamic-range</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/width\">width</a></li></ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>prefers-color-scheme</code></strong> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries#media_features\">media feature</a> is used to detect if the user has requested a light or dark color theme.</p>\n<p>The user might indicate this preference through an operating system setting (e.g. light or dark mode) or a user agent setting.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"light\"><code>light</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Indicates that user has notified that they prefer an interface that has a light theme, or has not expressed an active preference.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"dark\"><code>dark</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Indicates that user has notified that they prefer an interface that has a dark theme.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The elements below have an initial color theme. They can be further themed according to the user's color scheme preference.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>day<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Day (initial)<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>day light-scheme<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Day (changes in light scheme)<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>day dark-scheme<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Day (changes in dark scheme)<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>night<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Night (initial)<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>night light-scheme<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Night (changes in light scheme)<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>night dark-scheme<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Night (changes in dark scheme)<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.day</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #eee<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> black<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.night</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #333<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> white<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@media</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">prefers-color-scheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> dark<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">.day.dark-scheme</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #333<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> white<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"to